criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — sets the 10-year objective explicitly;  
Implement — uses PROJECT_LIFE to compute depreciation and terminal-year cash flows (NWC recovery and salvage);  
Reflect — reiterates project duration in the recommendation.

Discover — lists objective and parameterized project assumptions;  
Implement — uses those coded assumptions to build cash flows and metrics;  
Reflect — draws recommendation from model but does not justify the underlying real-estate/construction assumptions.
